<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Glopak Ambalaj</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }

    /* Company Information Section */
    .company-info {
      margin-top: 30px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .company-info h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .company-info p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Employee Section */
    .team-section {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .team-section h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .team-member {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .team-member img {
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-right: 20px;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
    }

    .team-member-info {
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .team-member-info h3 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .team-member-info p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .team-member-info a {
      color: #2980b9;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Return Button */
    .return-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .return-button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Glopak Ambalaj</h1>
      <p>Leading Packaging Solutions Since 1990</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Company Information Section -->
  <div class="container company-info">
    <h2>Our Company</h2>
    <p><strong>Founded:</strong> 1990</p>
    <p><strong>Customers Supplied:</strong> Over 5,000 satisfied businesses worldwide.</p>
    <p>At Glopak Ambalaj, we specialize in delivering high-quality packaging solutions to meet the diverse needs of our customers. From small businesses to large corporations, we are proud to support a wide range of industries.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <div class="container team-section">
    <h2>Our Team</h2>

    <!-- Team Member 1 -->
    <div class="team-member">
      <img src="/images/ceo.jpg" alt="CEO Photo" />
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <h3>John Doe</h3>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> CEO</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:john.doe@glopak.com">john.doe@glopak.com</a></p>
        <p>John has been leading Glopak Ambalaj since its founding and continues to drive the company's success in the global market.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Team Member 2 -->
    <div class="team-member">
      <img src="/images/worker1.jpg" alt="Worker 1 Photo" />
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Operations Manager</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:jane.smith@glopak.com">jane.smith@glopak.com</a></p>
        <p>Jane oversees day-to-day operations at Glopak, ensuring that our packaging solutions are delivered on time and to the highest standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Team Member 3 -->
    <div class="team-member">
      <img src="/images/worker2.jpg" alt="Worker 2 Photo" />
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <h3>Michael Brown</h3>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Lead Packaging Engineer</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:michael.brown@glopak.com">michael.brown@glopak.com</a></p>
        <p>Michael leads the engineering team at Glopak, constantly innovating new packaging technologies to better serve our clients.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Return to Dashboard Button -->
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="return-button">Return to Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Glopak Ambalaj - All Rights Reserved</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>